9 An Act relating to motor vehicles; amending 47 O.S.
2021, Section 1-171.1, which relates to street-legal
10 utility vehicles; modifying definition; amending 47
O.S. 2021, Section 11-1116, which relates to self-
11 propelled or motor-driven and operated vehicles;
updating statutory reference; authorizing use of
12 certain vehicles on certain U.S. Highways; and
providing an effective date.
